      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'm just not sure about the \"transparency\" part. if a customer sees \"in stock\" and then gets an email saying it's actually delayed, they're gonna feel lied to. honestly, the system is flagging our stock levels as critical right now. if i don't change the status to out-of-stock, aren't we basically just lying to them to keep the sales numbers up?",
